    LookDBF is plug-in for FAR manager 1.75 and higher.

It is intended for DBF-files viewing, edition and export.
ÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄ

Usage:
ÄÄÄÄÄÄÄ
   LookDBF may be started by FAR command line and by plug-in menu (F11) only.
For comfortable usage insert following command line into the "File Associations"
list:
               LookDBF:[options] !.!
Options:
   /d or /D - start with Dos code table (deafault is Win code table)
   /n or /N - show record numbers
   /m or /M - use full screen for memo showing
   /e or /E - permit edit, append and delete functions

Of course, you may change code table during LookDBF run.

