Create directory ...far\plugins\LookDBF and unzip LookDBF.zip into it.
Then reload FAR.

Functionality:
ÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄÄ
   LookDBF is "remake" of beautiful DBFView plug-in by Dmitry Volkov.
Unfortunantely, DBFView does not support of binary fields (DateTime, Integer,
Double, Currency), that Visual FoxPro 5.0 and higher generateing. This
circumstance and that I cannot contact with D.Volkov are causes of LookDBF
birth.

   LookDBF functions are listed below using following legend:

      + LookDBF only function, û both plug-ins function

û  Viewing DBF-file as a table using whole console screen;
û  Changing old and append new records
û  Search string in current field and in all of fields
+  Search records using condition
û  Mark interesting records using search and manually
û  Show interesting records only
û  Change columns viewing order
û  Change columns visible width
û  Hide and show columns
û  Rename columns
û  Export interesting records and visible columns in text, DBF or HTML form.
+  Visual FoxPro binary fields support
+  Mouse support
+  Console screen resizing support (Far 1.70 beta 5)
û  Save settings
û  Memo contents viewing
+  Long fields scrolling in visible column
+  Edit header of file.
+  Edit current field.
+  Search with replace.
+  Mask usage for search and replace.
+  DBF-files import
+  Sorting during export
+  Visual FoxPro nullable fields support
+  Visual FoxPro variable length fields support
+  FAR code tables support
+  Memo-file extension control

